1. *Stopa* se koristi za merenje dužine. (The foot is used to measure length.)
2. *Stope* su nam se umorile od hodanja. (Our feet are tired from walking.)
3. Moja visina je jedan metar i *šezdeset pet centimetara* ili *jedna stopa i petnaest inča*. (My height is one meter and sixty-five centimeters or one foot and fifteen inches.)
4. Povećana *stopa* nezaposlenosti ugrožava ekonomiju. (Increased unemployment rate is a threat to the economy.)
5. Da bi se smanjila emisija ugljen-dioksida, moramo smanjiti *stopu* sagorevanja fosilnih goriva. (In order to reduce carbon dioxide emissions, we must reduce the rate of burning fossil fuels.)
6. Molim vas, *stopirajte* ovaj voz za mene! (Please stop this train for me!)
7. Putnici su morali *da stopiraju* kako bi uhvatili poslednji autobus. (The passengers had to hitchhike in order to catch the last bus.)
8. Neki sportisti imaju brze *stope* od drugih. (Some athletes have faster feet than others.)
9. Vlada je odlučila da *stopira* planove za izgradnju novog aerodroma. (The government decided to put a halt to the plans for building a new airport.)
10. Iako je voz išao velikom *stopom*, kasnio je na svakoj stanici. (Although the train was going at a high speed, it was late at every station.)